Novartis AG (NOVN)  will appoint Mark Never
as new head of its German unit starting Nov. 1, Deutsche
Presseagentur reported, citing a company statement. Current
Germany chief Dirk Kosche will move to the oncology unit to lead
its emerging growth markets section. Never is currently head of
